<paragraph id="DAA7109D09878694BA8FEB6029CA8A7C" pageId="4" pageNumber="47">Medium-sized antlion with a variegated habitus, with an alternating ochre and dark brown pattern. Forewing Rs at half the wing length with at least 8 crossveins. Thorax covered with outstanding black and white setae. Tibia without spurs. Tarsus shorter than tibia.</paragraph>
